  • Type Parameters:
    E - a comparable class

    public class GeneralTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends com.muhammedokumus.BinaryTree
    A general tree class that extends BinaryTree class to add methods like add, search and print in different formats for generic trees.
